courseWork.description:
Submission
should include the following:
Network figure screenshot
Screenshots of BGP Configurations on
all three routers
Screenshot of pinging from one PC to another
(in the same network and in the different network)

courseWork.description:
Helping videos:

Basics of cisco packet tracer

how to assign IP, pinging: https://youtu.be/frUQMHXhnvs?si=xZ-u_nQGqridF1zP
switch: https://youtu.be/eFY6mi3lmRQ?si=2NiBpKU1W4IGAZeS
router: https://youtu.be/FnH1XUQsoD8?si=osB4-r8w8lWwc1ZI (must watch)
DHCP configuration in cisco packet tracer: https://youtu.be/DsL_JEdMPXg?si=Me77TNt1NxF_87RA

(.pkt is the extension of cisco packet tracer file)

(.pkt is the extension of cisco packet tracer file)
